events.name: 第一部ラスト　侵入

parameters: \n< Serena >...This should be the intended location...

\n< Serena >...I can't find the rope. Is it hidden in an
inconspicuous place?

\n< Serena >No, I still can't find it. Has it been found and
disposed of...?
\n< Serena >It turned out just as Master had instructed.

\n< Serena >There was a discussion about going back if the
rope had been disposed of...

\n< Serena >We can no longer afford to waste time by turning
back. Every minute and every second, I don't want
to leave Erika-sama among them.

\n< Serena >And... although it's a very unpleasant thought,
the public lynching. Right now, their attention
should be focused over there.

\n< Serena >This is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to
achieve infiltration. I can't let this chance slip
away.

\n< Serena >I wonder if it's about a distance of 30 people in
height to the bottom.

\n< Serena >I've never tried it before, but... if it's this
height, the impact of landing should be able to be
softened with an air cushion.

\n< Serena >The conversion and release of impact... If I don't
mistime it...
